Package burp.api.montoya.persistence

Interface PersistedList<T>

All Superinterfaces:
Collection<T>, Iterable<T>, List<T>
public interface PersistedList<T> extends List<T>
This interface represents a list that has been persisted in the project. The methods of this list operate on the underlying persisted data.
